short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SemanticFinder | In-browser Semantic Search via Transformers.js

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Semantic search right in your browser! Calculates segment embeddings and cosine similarity client-side without server-side inferencing, using transformers.js. Currently best in English but 50+ languages are supported too!

Web app: https://do-me.github.io/SemanticFinder/
GitHub: https://github.com/do-me/SemanticFinder
